      ms_seq_limit
        complex
        dist_complex
        (complex_partial_sum_seq
          (fun k : set => div_CSNo (exp_CSNo_nat z k) (factorial k)))
        l.


(** Explicit-limit version of the same closure statement: once a complex limit is
    exhibited for the exponential partial sums, `complex_exp z` is complex.
    Moved earlier than some wrapper declarations because the unconditional
    `complex_exp_in_complex` theorem uses it directly. **)
