        K add mul X0 addX0 smulX0 p a0 (fun i => u0 (x i))).
admit.
//GOD1PRF:638297 We may therefore apply Theorem 5 to $\mathrm{D}_{u}$, which shows that
claim h_s23_t7_theorem5_formal_call :
