admit.
//GOD1PRF:727343 \mathrm{P}^{\prime}-\mathrm{P}=\left(\lambda_{1}+\cdots+\lambda_{n}-1\right) .\left(\mathrm{O}-\mathrm{O}^{\prime}\right) . \tag{7}
