//GOD1PRF:796916 Moreover, the relation (11) shows that every element of L is a polynomial in X with coefficients in K (in the sense of § 26, section 1), i.e., that
claim h_s27_construction_s26_section1_formal_call :
  forall L0, forall add0 mul0:set -> set -> set, forall K0,
  forall m0 :e omega, forall x0:set -> set,
    commutative_ring L0 add0 mul0 -> subring L0 add0 mul0 K0 ->
    (forall i :e m0, x0 i :e L0) ->
    subring_generated_by L0 add0 mul0 K0 {x0 i|i :e m0}
    = {y :e L0|polynomial_in_ring_elements L0 add0 mul0 K0 m0 x0 y}.
apply god1_subring_generated_by_finite_family_is_polynomial_values.
claim h_s27_construction_generated_by_indeterminates :
  subring_generated_by (multivariate_polynomial_ring K add n)
    (polynomial_addition K add n) (polynomial_multiplication K add mul n)
