admit.
//GOD1PRF:864242 and is called the field of rational fractions in $n$ indeterminates over the field K . The elements of $\mathrm{K}\left(X_{1}, \ldots, \mathrm{X}_{n}\right)$ are called rational fractions in $n$ indeterminates with coefficients in K .
