//GOD1PRF:922045 from which (putting $\mathrm{T}=a$ ) we see that $f^{\prime}(a)=0$.\\
claim h_s30_t6_evaluation_conclusion :
  polynomial_root_multiplicity K add mul f a = 1
  <-> polynomial_evaluation K add mul K add mul 1 f (fun i => a)
        = ring_zero K add
